node.text:
Come out for a day of fun, food - and Dr. Pol! - at the Isabella County Fairgrounds in Mt. Pleasant, MI on Saturday, September 11 from 12pm - 4pm. Enjoy a meet & greet with Dr. Pol and Diane, and visit a variety of local vendors, food trucks and displays. 

At 1:30pm, there will be a memorial for 9/11 and a special presentation with Dr. Pol.

Admission is free for the event. There will be vendors with items for sale.

We’ll see ya! #drpol #drpol50 #drpolooza
